{"tid":714800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民調: 澳洲人相信「習近平」多於「特朗普」","createTime":"2018-06-24T02:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T11:51:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"409aee62607bdc4d96a83cf3a5cbd3b5f49b11cf","tid":714800,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲人對國家元首的支持度<br />\n<br />\n Theresa May (68%)<br />\n 安倍晉三 (66%)<br />\n Emmanuel Macron (61%)<br />\n 習近平 (43%)<br />\n Donald Trump (30%)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-06-20/australians-put-more-trust-in-china-s-xi-than-donald-trump?utm_content=business&amp;utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;cmpid=socialflow-twitter-business&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-06-20%2Faustralians-put-more-trust-in-china-s-xi-than-donald-trump%3Futm_content%3Dbusiness%26utm_campaign%3Dsocialflow-organic%26cmpid%3Dsocialflow-twitter-business%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial&d=qGEn258Ii1sbyQSJeHwt0UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d071e852\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-06-20/australians-put-more-trust-in-china-s-xi-than-donald-trump?utm_content=business&amp;utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;cmpid=socialflow-twitter-business&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span><br />\n<br />\npolitics<br />\nAustralians Trust Xi More Than Trump, Survey Says<br />\n<br />\nSurvey finds only 30% expect U.S. leader to &lsquo;do right thing&rsquo;<br />\nRespondents have faith in alliance; worry about China meddling<br />\n<br />\nBy Jason Scott<br />\nJune 20, 2018, 9:01 AM GMT+8<br />\n<br />\nAustralians have less confidence in President Donald Trump than Chinese counterpart Xi Jinping, but remain convinced that the U.S. alliance is vital for the country&rsquo;s security, according to a survey.<br />\n<br />\nAbout 30 percent of Australians have confidence Trump will &ldquo;do the right thing in world affairs,&rdquo; according to an annual Lowy Institute survey released Wednesday. The U.S. commander-in-chief comes seventh out the nine leaders ranked in the survey, behind U.K. Prime Minister Theresa May (68 percent) and Xi (43 percent) and ahead of Russia&rsquo;s Vladimir Putin (19 percent) and North Korea&rsquo;s Kim Jong Un (5 percent)."},{"pid":"56bb9438d838486efd2d8539469970c815dd6722","tid":714800,"uid":12021,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"098feb0214ef77cdd422bddf16808bbc1139fcc0","tid":714800,"uid":94819,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b962b436dfde98200711c9906ed1d10481c7a74","tid":714800,"uid":142888,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會係班華僑搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似有個2003年移民澳洲嘅大陸人做咗國會議員，之後上電視話當年64事件，解放軍屠殺班學生係啱。結果俾人屌佢違反澳洲人嘅價值觀，叫佢返大陸人"},{"pid":"c8e6d3f92697539addc5fc4e160afe62ccd2383e","tid":714800,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係班華僑搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似有個2003年移民澳洲嘅大陸人做咗國會議員，之後上電視話當年64事件，解放軍屠殺班學生係啱。結果俾人屌佢違反澳洲<del><span style=\"color: red;\">人</span></del>嘅價值觀，叫佢返大陸<del><span style=\"color: red;\">人</span></del></blockquote>"},{"pid":"50bfcdc054978fb9a17142b542497caaa9c47378","tid":714800,"uid":59283,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:26:14.000Z","msg":"個民調係咪係china town做"},{"pid":"999e405a572cb4ae9e1c9983434214639dbf8d1d","tid":714800,"uid":23170,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"屌，澳洲大撚把大中華膠，嗰時我個lecturer都係大中華膠，係咁講話自己去中國出trip有幾咁偉大，發展得有幾咁快。又係咁講啲中文字，又